org.cef.callback

接口 CefURLRequestClient

  • 所有超级接口:
    CefNative 

    public interface CefURLRequestClient
extends CefNative
    Interface that should be implemented by the CefURLRequest client. The methods of this class will be called on the same thread that created the request unless otherwise documented. (CefURLRequest客户端应实现的接口。除非另有说明，否则将在创建请求的同一线程上调用此类的方法。)

    • 方法详细资料

      • getAuthCredentials

        boolean getAuthCredentials(boolean isProxy,
                           java.lang.String host,
                           int port,
                           java.lang.String realm,
                           java.lang.String scheme,
                           CefAuthCallback callback)
        Called on the IO thread when the browser needs credentials from the user. |isProxy| indicates whether the host is a proxy server. |host| contains the hostname and |port| contains the port number. Return true to continue the request and call CefAuthCallback::Continue() when the authentication information is available. Return false to cancel the request. This method will only be called for requests initiated from the browser process. (当浏览器需要用户的凭据时，在IO线程上调用。 | isProxy |指示主机是否是代理服务器。 |主机|包含主机名和| port |包含端口号。返回true以继续请求，并在身份验证信息可用时调用CefAuthCallback :: Continue（）。返回false取消请求。仅对从浏览器进程发起的请求调用此方法。)

      • onDownloadData

        void onDownloadData(CefURLRequest request,
                    byte[] data,
                    int data_length)
        Called when some part of the response is read. |data| contains the current bytes received since the last call. This method will not be called if the UR_FLAG_NO_DOWNLOAD_DATA flag is set on the request. (读取响应的某些部分时调用。 |数据|包含自上次调用以来收到的当前字节。如果在请求上设置了UR_FLAG_NO_DOWNLOAD_DATA标志，则不会调用此方法。)

      • onDownloadProgress

        void onDownloadProgress(CefURLRequest request,
                        int current,
                        int total)
        Notifies the client of download progress. |current| denotes the number of bytes received up to the call and |total| is the expected total size of the response (or -1 if not determined). (通知客户端下载进度。 |当前|表示直到调用为止接收到的字节数，并且| total |是预期的响应总大小（如果未确定，则为-1）。)

      • onRequestComplete

        void onRequestComplete(CefURLRequest request)
        Notifies the client that the request has completed. Use the CefURLRequest::GetRequestStatus method to determine if the request was successful or not. (通知客户端请求已完成。使用CefURLRequest :: GetRequestStatus方法确定请求是否成功。)

      • onUploadProgress

        void onUploadProgress(CefURLRequest request,
                      int current,
                      int total)
        Notifies the client of upload progress. |current| denotes the number of bytes sent so far and |total| is the total size of uploading data (or -1 if chunked upload is enabled). This method will only be called if the UR_FLAG_REPORT_UPLOAD_PROGRESS flag is set on the request. (通知客户端上传进度。 |当前|表示到目前为止已发送的字节数，并且| total |是上传数据的总大小（如果启用了分块上传，则为-1）。仅在请求上设置了UR_FLAG_REPORT_UPLOAD_PROGRESS标志时，才会调用此方法。)
